’Щ@2fbebe2db51122d15785ab2d614dde15c9af729fcfced5e848a1fb3f91db75abЪЇTitle: title: str title-case
Path: Examples
Content:
convert a string to Title Case
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'nu-shell' | str title-case
Nu Shell

```
convert a string to Title Case
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'this is a test case' | str title-case
This Is A Test Case

```
convert a column from a table to Title Case
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[title, count]; ['nu test', 100]] | str title-case title
